column5: Hopefully next year will be even better ! ...a few 60 inch Niagara muskies will help  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSnqwobOxhg
Cool Video RLFT Looks like your season's been a riot Thanks for sharing Leechman

Thanks ...I have a ton of footage from the year but I tried to keep it short.  Whoever PM'd me....(sorry, deleted it before I could reply)...yes, all of the footage was taken from Niagara.  Upper and lower Niagara river, and Erie.  Gotta love Southern Ontario
Awesome vid    That part behind the snow machine....hilarious!! Love watching your vids

Hahaha...I know, I took my life in my hands that day. I was sweating so bad by the time we got out to the spot because I was holding on for dear life hahahaha. Caught lots of perch though so I guess it was worth it
